Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Remind me how this\Nhappened again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And why there's a\Ngiant turtle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,eatin' my family's\Nentire summer crop?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. Mr. Tortasnap\Nsaid he was hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but he promised me he would\Nonly take a few small bites!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that thing\Nknows what "small" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[yanks] Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Spikey-Wikey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack and Pinkie,\Nyou distract him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, Rarity, and\NFluttershy, let's save Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:01:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tortasnap, I'm only asking\Nnicely once. Let my friend GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [trumpet fanfare] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And now a simple\Nteleportation spell should...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt, interloper!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [trumpet fanfare] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back, friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister and I will\Ntake care of the beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All the times we've\Nactually needed their help,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and they show up for {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what\NI was about to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Goodness, sister,\Nthat was FUN!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to thank us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, we've\Nrecently realized
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we like being part\Nof the action!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Experiencing life instead\Nof just dreaming about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And making a difference\Noutside the throne room!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all think they're gonna\Nbe doin' this a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! We'd better ask\Nsomepony to fix that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna:\NWhich is why... we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I can't\Nread this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to\Nlead a Filly Guides hike
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,if the map makes\Nus MORE lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia:\NDid somepony say... lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna:\NNot for long! Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[slurp]\N-Oh, now this is just terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Cheerilee ordered\Ncupcakes for school today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I forgot to\Nmake the order!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no biggie!\NWe can just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Students going hungry?\NNot on our watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us bake, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack:\NAnd then they {\i1}carried{\i0} Granny\NSmith across the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't even\Nany traffic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that we don't\Nappreciate their help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But suddenly Celestia\Nand Luna seem to think
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't do anything\Non our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to learn\Nto be rulers of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with them fixing every\Nteensy problem for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the Princesses\Nchanged their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they don't think we're\Nup to the responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of protecting\NEquestria after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe this week's\Njust a one-time thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that'll never\Nhappen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! A strategy meeting! What\Nis the danger this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A rampaging beast? Evil\Nspell? Friendship problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready to do\Nwhatever we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. But is\Nsomething wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, you've been helping\Nus an awful lot and we know
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you have way more important\Nruler-y things to do, so.....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We've spent more than enough\Ntime in the throne room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Real life is\Nhappening out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's what\Nthis is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sick of\Nbeing princesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly. Battling\Nthe Everfree Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,alongside Starswirl\Nmade us realize
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what we've missed out on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of spending\Nthe day ruling..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And the night\Npatrolling dreams..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted a chance to\Ndo the things {\i1}you{\i0} do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the day. Adventure with\Nfriends! Shampoo anteaters...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure Fluttershy is\Nthe only pony that does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are {\i1}way{\i0}\Nmore fun things to do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,than.. follow us around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! You should make a list of\Nall the stuff you never tried
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but always wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lotta little\Nthings out there to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What an intriguing idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Only, it's much harder\Nto justify a vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from the castle\Nwhen it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,an "emergency"\Nwe're responding to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We'll cover\Nyour palace duties!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a good chance\Nfor us to practice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for when you retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're sure you\Ndon't mind the extra effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pshh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief to know the\NRoyal Swanifying Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is in good hooves. Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fun Not Yet Had".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! I can't wait to start\Nplanning our time off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance to do\Nwhatever we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know\Nwhat that means!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Adventure!\NRelaxation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just that\NI.. I spend each night
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in everypony's\Nintense dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So I could use some\Nreal-world downtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I understand. But for me,\Nevery day IS real-world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Meetings and decrees, and\Nmeetings about decrees,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and decrees about the\Nmeetings. I crave excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. I'm not sure how we\Ncan both be happy. Unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We take turns\Ndoing what we like!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have the perfect\Naccessories for us to wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! [uncertain laugh]\NWe'll be...Twinsies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like regular\Npony tourists!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd\Nlove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a few things\Nfor us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunglasses, bug\Nspray, ice boots,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,hoof sanitizer, and travel\Nsnacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to add water...\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect,\NSister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And here are instructions\Nof how to prepare
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Royal Swanifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's written down, I'm sure\Nwe can handle it. Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing. We're\Nleaving you in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of raising the sun and\Nmoon while we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We have put a small part of\Nour power in this amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can activate it with\Nyour magic at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Preferably dawn and dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! That's not a terrifying\Nlevel of responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you\Ndown, princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me that\Nscroll says what
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the Royal Swanifying is!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it's a\Ncelebration of all the swans
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in the royal lake.\NWe round 'em up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,parade 'em through\Nthe streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and finish with a\Nparty in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,One question. WHY?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance to\Nshow Celestia and Luna
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll do whatever\Nthe job requires.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If they can take care\Nof all this themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,then I know we\Ncan, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Jolly good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are definitely not\Nreading the scroll I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, sister,\Nfrom now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we are regular,\Ncare-free ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving the\Nprincess life behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're not even\Ngoing to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! How\Nnew and different!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like\NPinkie Pie said.
