Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ There's a lotta little{\i0}\N{\i1} things you gotta try ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Just a pack of punchy plunges{\i0}\N{\i1} other ponies all take ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ That have princess-pony{\i0}\N{\i1} passed us right by ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Nopony knows you like{\i0}\N{\i1} your little sister ♪{\i0}
