Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You can't venture on{\i0}\N{\i1} adventures ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ if you're taking a nap ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You can't check things{\i0}\N{\i1} off your checklist ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ while you sleep ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So let's take another hill ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Sometimes you can be a pill ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And why's the way{\i0}\N{\i1} ahead always so steep? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[music ends]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Princesses, we are\Nhere to... Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Er. We're fillin' in\Nfor Their Majesties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we help\Ny'all with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I say. How irregular. Well,\Nthen, we offer our assistance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as heads of the Royal\NSwanifying committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. But we\Nhave it all covered!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really{\i0}...? Well. Good\Nluck with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ask for help,\Nit's just like admitting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not as good at the job\Nas Luna and Celestia are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, how hard can\Nthrowing a "Swan Party" be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! All we have\Nleft to do is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Polish the armor, bubble the\Npunch, glitter the carpets,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,puff the pastry,\Nfloat the floats,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and carpet every\Nroad in Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I keep reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Celestia, since we're\Nboth a little tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe the first thing we\Ndo shouldn't be.. too wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what I\Nwas thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,ZIP LINE...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now every time we have tea, we\Ncan remember this magical day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad you\Nenjoyed yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, we're going\Nto do something
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but never could, because\Nof my night shift!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it another zip-line!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the post office!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think! All the mail in\NPonyville goes through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One stamp, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for it.....!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't need a stamp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,if you were just going\Nto give this to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes but, {\i1}I{\i0} didn't\Ngive it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A mailpony took it from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,searched to find who it was\Nmeant for, and gave it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the PROCESS!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[echoing] Did you know that\Nnopony has ever explored
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the bottom of\Nthese caverns?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[cracking rock]\NI wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to try this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this wonderful, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ There's a lotta little things{\i0}\N{\i1} you gotta do in this world ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ There's a lotta little{\i0}\N{\i1} things you oughta view ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And our little lotta lists{\i0}\N{\i1} may be a little bit long ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And might take a{\i0}\N{\i1} lotta bother to do ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But I'm sure it gets{\i0}\N{\i1} better, later on ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And after darkest{\i0}\N{\i1} night's, a new dawn ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ It's my turn to{\i0}\N{\i1} do the choosing ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ After river rapid cruising ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ This adventure isn't{\i0}\N{\i1} too fun to be..... on ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [busy music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It has come to our attention\Nthat you don't intend
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to serve watercress at the\NRoyal Swanifying Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not enough in\Nthe castle kitchens to--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me. Tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you must do something\Nabout the garbage
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,piling up outside! The street\Nsweepers are on strike
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and the royal carpeters\Ncan't do their jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you even know there were\Nroyal street carpeters?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. I do hope those\Naren't the {\i1}final{\i0} decorations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,for the gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your\Nconstructive criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't really\Nhave time to chat so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [soft music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope {\i1}you're{\i0}\Nenjoying yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,on your super-relaxing\Npicnic, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be, if you\Nhadn't made us hike
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,through a million\NPRICKLE BUSHES.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they hurt less than\Nthat horrible howling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you dragged us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Ponyliacci\Nand it's an OPERA!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you made us\Nleave early,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,even though it\Nwas still my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just face it, Luna.\NYou are NEVER happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't\Nwant me to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I always have to\Ndo things {\i1}your{\i0} way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you wish I'd\Nnever come back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so you could still\Nrule day AND night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I LIKE that\Nkind of pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Being responsible for\Nevery little thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in Equestria AND you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'd LIKE is a\Nsister I can depend on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU MEAN BOSS AROUND?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,CALM DOWN, LUNA!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No! And don't you dare use\Nyour Canterlot voice on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this adventure\Nwould be better
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,if I did it by MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,FINE! I just remembered\Nsomething I forgot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to\Ndo. Be! Alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we have the same thing\Non both of our lists then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [busy music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie! You got\Nthose appetizers yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Still mashing\Nthe guacamole!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're just going\Nhave to do with sequins!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, sorry for\Nthe bad news,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but the courtyard is full\Nof swans waiting to get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're nowhere\Nnear ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How do Celestia and\NLuna rule a kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,AND get all this done by\Nthemselves every year!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha. Oh, how droll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what's the funny\Npart, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The princesses never do\Nall the ceremony planning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They...don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the gala\Nplanning committees are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony could\Nhandle all {\i1}this{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those...sequins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Still rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! New plan, everypony!\NWe're going to delegate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You're on food duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I need gemstones...\Nand purple satin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the ponies\Nat the gates
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's a slight\Ndelay on the gala!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, if it's not too\Nmuch trouble, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Now who can we get to\Nclean up all this garbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm delegating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So THIS is how you\Nrule Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh. Things are so\Nmuch more relaxing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,without my bossy sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who needs a gloomy sister
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,moping around all\Nthe time anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, princess. Didn't\Nyou wear {\i1}any{\i0} sunblock?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a thing? Celestia\Nwould have warned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,if she were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Now, was it two left\Nturns and a right,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,or two right\Nturns and a left?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna always handled\Ndirections!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [horror sting] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [heavy music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[nervously] And scared away..\Nthe chickens!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I thought climbing Mt.\NFillymanejaro was on MY list.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not copying you. I just\Nwanted to watch the sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'm...here for\Nthe moonset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, how did the\Nrest of your day go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, amazing. Yeah. Fantastic.\NBest ever, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Me... too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You, you... can walk with me.\NYou know, if you want, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well. Since we're\Ngoing the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is SO beautiful. It must\Nbe amazing in the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The night's pretty\Nspecial, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me to look for\Nthose when I was a filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[soft laugh] Hope I wasn't\Ntoo {\i1}bossy{\i0} doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, being with your\Nsister all the time is hard but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,being without\Nher? It's even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I do know. And I\Nwouldn't trade you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for any of the\Nadventures on my list.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even your Zip-line?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even my Zip-line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I said\Nthose things before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's just...tough\Nbeing the little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not always easy being\Nthe big sister, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The sun and the moon\Ntogether...at the same time!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now where have I\Nseen THAT before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [bright music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You think maybe\NTwilight's having trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,with the amulet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably\Ngo help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, OK! I think\NI got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst says we just need to\Nreset the amulet with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the screw on the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...no more than one half turn..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anypony have some tape!?
